16 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 70 O.S. 2021, Section 24-100.4, as
17 amended by Section 6, Chapter 15, O.S.L. 2023 (70 O.S. Supp. 2024,
18 Section 24-100.4), is amended to read as follows:
19 Section 24-100.4. A. Each school district board of education
20 shall adopt a policy for the discipline of all children attending
21 public school in that district, and for the investigation of
22 reported incidents of bullying. The policy shall provide options
23 for the discipline of the students and shall define standards of
