10 disciplinary action shall be taken solely on the basis of an
11 anonymous report;
12 3. Contain a requirement that any school employee that has
13 reliable information that would lead a reasonable person to suspect
14 that a person is a target of bullying shall immediately report it to
15 the principal or a designee of the principal;
16 4. Contain a statement of how the policy is to be publicized
17 including a requirement that:
18 a. an annual written notice of the policy be provided to
19 parents, guardians, staff, volunteers, and students,
20 with age-appropriate language for students,
21 b. notice of the policy be posted at various locations
